properties.name: Cafe by Wolfgang Puck at Springs Preserve
properties.description: Posted by Snoopyk9 I know, I know...Wolfgang Puck. Some of you may feel ecstatic, thinking of fancy gourmet cuisine...some of you roll your eyes, thinking of the cans of soup you find in the supermarket. But this place is amazing. Kobe beef cheeseburger is such an amazing experience. I\'ve heard that some of his other restaurants might not live up to his name and the expectations of a celebrity chef restaurant. But this place does.

properties.name: Chow Bar
properties.description: Posted by Snoopyk9 216 S Indiana Ave Bloomington, IN 47408Delicious Chinese food in Bloomington. My number 1 choice when I\'m in town. We love the noodle soups, cold noodles, and twice cooked pork. I also love their Sunday buffet. Dou jiang, pig\'s feet, crispy skin pork, roast duck. You can\'t get more authentic than that.

properties.name: Corky's Ribs & BBQ
properties.description: Posted by Snoopyk9 100 Franklin Road, Brentwood TN 37027If I remember correctly, just off I-65, south of Nashville, TN is Corky\'s (although I thought the name was Porky\'s). One of my top 5 of BBQ joints. They have dry and wet rub and all the sides are delicious!

properties.name: Gibson's BBQ
properties.description: Posted by Snoopyk9 3319 Memorial Huntsville, AL 35801Great BBQ in Huntsville. Went there with my honey\'s family. Not a fan of hushpuppies (anywhere).

properties.name: Lao Sze Chuan
properties.description: Posted by Snoopyk9 2172 S Archer Ave , Chicago , IL Best Chinese food in Chicago. There\'s always a long wait, but it\'s well worth it. We love the string beans and ma po tofu.

properties.name: Lucky Express
properties.description: Posted by Snoopyk9 307 E 3rd St Bloomington, IN 47401My number two for delicious Chinese food in Bloomington. It doesn\'t seem like much, but I can pretty much go in and order whatever I\'d like an they\'ll make it.

properties.name: Manny's Pollo
properties.description: Posted by Snoopyk9 1000 N 7th St Leavenworth, KS 66048Best restaurant in Leavenworth. Love the carnitas burritos and tacos...and the tamales!

properties.name: Oklahoma Joe's
properties.description: Posted by Snoopyk9 3002 W. 47th Avenue, Kansas City, KS 66103Best KC BBQ!

properties.name: Sonny's BBQ
properties.description: Posted by Snoopyk9 3635 S.W. Archer Rd., Gainesville, FLA BBQ chain in the south. Delicious! We stopped off here on our way through Florida. It was one of the best BBQ places.

properties.name: Springs Preserve
properties.description: Posted by Snoopyk9 333 S. Valley View, Las Vegas, NVI had my wedding here and it is absolutely gorgeous. Who\'d have thought that Las Vegas would have a botanical garden. The grounds are absolutely amazing and are a pretty comprehensive display of the beauty of the desert in one little place. The best part is that being there makes you forget that you are in Sin City.
